cs3500.music.view

Class MockSynthesizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs3500.music.view.MockSynthesizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, javax.sound.midi.MidiDevice, javax.sound.midi.Synthesizer

    public class MockSynthesizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.sound.midi.Synthesizer
    Mocks a MIDI synthesizer for testing purposes. Produces a mock receiver that modifies this objects string builder object.

        public MockSynthesizer(java.lang.Appendable log)
